:: BrambleEvent {"position":"1700,1400","size":"100,100"}
You notice a matchstick deep within a cluster of thorny brush.<br>
<br>
You're not sure if you can reach it unscathed, but the match could prove useful.

<div class="options">
[[Reach for the match-><%= chance("BrambleEventFail", "BrambleEventSuccess", 3) %>]]<br>
[[Leave it->BrambleEventLeave]]
</div>


:: BrambleEventFail {"position":"1700,1200","size":"100,100"}
<% damage(1) %>
You reach for the match, but you hesitate and the thorns cut a gash in your arm.<br>
<br>
You get the match, but at a cost.<br>
<br>
<%= dyingDead(
"You're able to walk just fine, but you're a bit worse for wear.",
"As you walk away you begin to feel lightheaded.<br><br>You fall to the ground with a thud."
) %>

<div class="options">
<%= dyingDead(
"[[Continue onwards->StepUp]]",
"[[Pass out->GameOver]]"
) %>
</div>


:: BrambleEventLeave {"position":"1950,1200","size":"100,100"}
You leave the match alone.<br>
<br>
Not much worth the risk, you think.

<div class="options">
[[Continue onwards->StepUp]]
</div>


:: BrambleEventSuccess {"position":"1825,1200","size":"100,100"}
