:: WendigoEvent {"position":"1300,1400","size":"100,100"}
A tall monstrous creature appears before you.<br>
<br>
Its glowing red eyes stare you down through its skull-like head.<br>
<br>
It looks hungry.

<div class="options">
[[Try to maneuver around it-><%= chance("WendigoEventFail", "WendigoEventSuccess", 2) %>]]<br>
<%= returnIfMatches("[[Use a match->WendigoEventMatch]]") %>
</div>


:: WendigoEventFail {"position":"1300,1200","size":"100,100"}
<% damage(1) %>
As you run past it you feel a sharp pain in your side.<br>
<br>
You manage to escape, but when you look down you notice blood trickling from your shirt.<br>
<br>
<%= dyingDead(
"You are still alive, for now.",
"You begin to feel lightheaded and fall to the ground."
) %>

<div class=options>
<%= dyingDead(
"[[Continue onwards->StepUp]]",
"[[Pass out->GameOver]]"
) %>
</div>


